Install:

sudo zypper in rubygem-rails-4_1 rubygem-sqlite3 rubygem-gettext_rails rubygem-nokogiri memcached

Additional gems either from devel:languages:ruby:extensions (incompatible atm) or rubygems:
daemons, mongrel, ruby-debug, delayed_job (1.8.4), capistrano


cat > config/database.yml <<EOF
development:
  adapter: sqlite3
  database: db/development.sqlite3
  pool: 5
  timeout: 5000
EOF

rake db:migrate

git submodule init
git submodule update


Generating a secret token:

* cp config/secrets.yml.example config/secrets.yml
* Generate a new secret with 'rake -s secret' and replace secret_key_base keys in config/secrets.yml


rails s
